Sikkim earthquake : Bollywood in mourning New Delhi , Sep 19 , ( IANS ) : Amitabh Bachchan , Kabir Bedi , Karan Johar and Rahul Bose are among the Bollywood twitterati who have mourned the loss of lives in Sikkim , which was hit by a powerful earthquake that left at least 23 people dead and 200 injured .